Cell["\<\
Substitution of SingletPolarizationLevel and PolarizationLevel in simulation \
routines disabled. The rotation of rules in Signal1D, etc., was causing a \
conflict with the tricky handling of multidimensional variables in \
EnsembleAverage. \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.700565868871554*^9, 3.700565907054174*^9}, {
